# MyGaragePro

Before coding: read `AGENTS.md` → `docs/PROGRESS.md` (decision log) → `docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md`. Module work → `docs/*_MODULE.md`. Spec sections → `docs/PROJECT_PLAN.md` as needed.

## Do not invent

Requirements come from chat + PROGRESS decision log + module docs + PROJECT_PLAN + existing code. No new fields, endpoints, or business rules without agreement.

## Tenancy & auth

- `garageAccountId` from `RequestUser` only — never from client body.
- `@UseGuards(PermissionsGuard)` + `@RequirePermissions` on API routes.
- `user.enabledModules.includes(...)` in services.
- UI permissions hide buttons only; server enforces.

## Data & finance

- Soft delete (`deletedAt`); audit meaningful mutations.
- `prisma.$transaction` for multi-table / money / stock writes.
- Ledger rules: copy invoice/ledger services; every money event posts to ledger.

## Monorepo

- Types in `packages/shared`; rebuild shared before typecheck.
- Mirror **customers** module for new entities (module → service → controller → dto → mapper).
- Smallest correct diff; no unrelated refactors.

## Done checklist

Tenancy scoped · permissions on routes · shared types/migration if API changed · `pnpm typecheck` · update PROGRESS decision log if rules changed.
